707017f-a.title: Brooklyn: Sutter Ave. - Sheridan Ave.
707017f-a.text:
(1)
Sutter Ave., at the N.E. corner of Sheridan Ave., (showing an old
house which the photographer states is on Old Mill Road (Plunders Neck
Road), about two blocks south of New Lots Road. In the right back-
ground is P.S. No. 159.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
(2)
The same, another view.
1922.
